description: Are you looking for the finest smoothies in all of Albuquerque? Then there's nobody roaming the streets who's better than Green Growler Smoothies! To help you lead a healthier and more amazing life, this smoothie truck is serving up fresh and organic smoothies made perfect for you. Green Growler Smoothies are bringing you smoothies to not just survive, but thrive!
name: Green Growler Smoothies
